@node Introduct
Introduction
~~~~~~~~~~~~
ViewPNM is an image viewer for PICASSO II gfxboards. It  displays  PPM
(24  Bit),  PGM  (8  Bit  Grey)  and PBM (1 Bit) files produced by the
picture converter/manipulator tools from the PBM, PBMPLUS  and  NETPBM
libraries (Available on Aminet or sundry CD-Roms).
@endnode

